1. *Scena* je bila veoma zanimljiva (The scene was very interesting).
2. On je imao *scenu* sa direktorom (He had a scene with the director).
3. *Sceni* su obično dugački (The scenes are usually long).
4. On je napravio *scenu* u kafani (He made a scene in the café).
5. Ona je ispratila *scenu* sa plačem (She ended the scene with tears).